These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, montecristo, oliveros, swisher
1. the montecristo-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the swisher-smoker is between the bluemaster-smoker and the montecristo-smoker##2
3. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | swisher | montecristo | oliveros |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, card-games, sudoku, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Hobby   | card-games | chess | rock-climbing | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
