2. the aristoff-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the montecristo-smoker is between the old-henry-smoker and the blend-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Cigar   | aristoff | old-henry | montecristo | blend |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, rock-climbing, drawing, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | photography | board-games | drawing |

