2. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Flower   | poppy | amaryllis | azalea | zinnia |

