2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2       |     3      |  4   |
| Transport   | tram | trike | jet-ski | roller |

