3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
4. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | motorbike | roller | ship |

